						               													<description>Godsland &amp;ndash; A board game which unites 5 mythologies: Greek, Egyptian, Norse, Chinese and Georgian. Choose your favorite mythology and lead your nation to victory. Use mythical creatures and other warriors to conquer lands and become the only ruler of this world. Bring glory to your nation by wise and proper strategy plans. NO LUCK! Everything is in your hands! Nothing limits your decisions. The only limit is your enemy. You will feel the real taste of strategy game when you rule the country based on your skills and not luck. 3D miniature figures, different boards, effective system for controlling resources, tokens, different cards. all this in one game &amp;ndash; Godsland!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game you will have to make decisions as you have different options: taking resources, recruiting soldiers, attacking neighbor territories, selling different resources to get more gold, upgrading villages, breaking and building bridges, using god&amp;rsquo;s powers, mythical creatures&amp;#10;It is crucial to have a good strategy in this game as everything depends on you. To become the mighty ruler you will have to control at least 15 territories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Beside your warriors you will have to use mythical creatures to defeat your enemies. During the game you will get some cards where can be blessing or fury from your gods. Those might help you for achieving your goals or on the opposite benefit your enemies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
